{
  "stem": "1938.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 441.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I, I can say that I was lucky till the time came that the World, the Second World War broke out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before the war broke out--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "-- I understood that I helped my parents in any direction in the house, in the profession.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, it was the most-- because the Bedzin city contained from just the most Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, I cannot recall that I was anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when I was in public school, I had many very disappointments.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I was little girl, when it comes Passover, then you have new clothes, which was a custom.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And non-Jewish kids passed by and spit at me or throw me a stone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I went to the religious school beside the, the main city, I had thrown a stone covered with snow in my hat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was very depressed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The last days before the war broke out was impossible, was-- the anti-Semitism was rising in Poland very badly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And our life was in, really, jeopardy because they were breaking the windows of the stores, of the Jewish stores.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was impossible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we are-- we were very used to a hard life, considering-- like, Holland or other countries, Belgium, when came to our concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were used to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we are the one, we, we could take more than the others.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The others usually, they failed after a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were dying out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The nature of Poland Jews was very-- willpower.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A strong willpower we had.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Willpower to live.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Born willpower.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But me, as, as I was a one child, was really hard when I was taking-- I was working for the Wehrmacht, for the German.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- when the war start, we looked out the window.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
